title: Frozen rectal tumor sample (B1124)
extract_protocol_ch1: DNA was isolated with the Genomic Wizard Kit (Promega)
label_protocol_ch1: Biotinylated DNA wase prepared according to the standard Affymetrix protocol for Affymetrix 10K SNP arrays
hyb_protocol: Hybridisation according to the protocol for Affymetrix 10K SNP arrays
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the GeneChip® Scanner 3000
data_processing: Genotypes were scored with the GDAS software (Affymetrix). Copy numbers were consequently computed with dCHIP SNP and CNAG. Samples were normalized against a set of in-house normal reference samples.
